creator: Edwin Arlington Robinson
description:
LibriVox recording of The Three Taverns: A Book of Poems by Edwin Arlington Robinson.
Read in English by J. Olpecre; John Burlinson; Jude; Carol; Sonia; Tony Addison; Connor Anderson; George Allen; Jacquelyn Bengfort
This is a volume of poems by Edwin Arlington Robinson. This volume contains, among other poems, the famous poems The Valley of the Shadow and Lazarus. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
